{
	"_source": "design/gdd/terrain-system.md",
	"_notes": [
		"wet_affected: GDD terrain table marks Road and Village as 'No change' in seasons,",
		"so the Wet x1.5 multiplier applies only to types with wet_affected=true.",
		"Movement cost is ceil(base_cost * multiplier): Ford 2->3 AP, Bridge 1->2 AP in Wet (per GDD river rules).",
		"attacker_ranged_mod applies when attacking FROM this terrain (Hill +25%).",
		"defender_ranged_mod applies when the TARGET stands on this terrain (Forest -25%, Village -15%, Bridge/Ford cover equivalent to Village).",
		"attacker_melee_mod: Hill -10% melee.",
		"defense_mod: defender defense bonus while occupying (Village +15%, Bridge +15%).",
		"crossing_defense_mod: penalty while mid-crossing a Ford (-20%)."
	],
